

This example illustrates how to customize actions
when retrieved selection results.

  The example use two tables: ORDERS and CUSTOMER,
which are usually included in the sample data sources
of ODBC. If you want to run the example on your
own data souce which does not contain, you can create 
create them and fill them with data by yourself, 
their structures look like:

CUSTOMER: --- custid --- company --- ......

ORDERS: ---- orderid --- custid ---- ......
